      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly incredible, flawless condition\u2014it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! Whether you're cruising on the weekend or commuting in style, you won't find one better cared for. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
