    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior still retains that distinctive new-car scent. Every stitch in the premium leather is perfect, and the seat bolsters show no signs of entry wear. Mechanically, it is flawless; the engine purrs with precision, and the gear shifts are seamless. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and meticulously maintained with a documented full service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously curated piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
