      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. It has been maintained to an exacting standard, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original showroom character. Mechanical integrity is absolute, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
