    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been parked in a garage its whole life. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
