      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This chassis is mechanically flawless, having received documented subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension maintains factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original depth with zero paint imperfections or oxidative wear. A true turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
